[Student "S"]
{With eleven cards in the "round" suits NORTH has a lot of playing strength. So when SOUTH bids 
a Limit Raise in \Hs NORTH wants to know about Aces.

RKCBlackwood tells him that SOUTH has two Aces plus the trump Queen, so NORTH can see that 6\H 
is practically a certainty.}

